incident_updates.body: A fix has been identified and is being rolled out across the platform.

Some services are experiencing intermittent restarts at elevated rates due to sporadic failures of underlying resources. While stateless services without an attached disk typically recover quickly, stateful services take longer to fully restart due to the need to guarantee data integrity during this process. Engineering is investigating the cause of the elevated rate of failure of underlying resources.
